  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Beauty Branch Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>We are expanding and continuously looking out for talents with growth mindset to join our fun and dynamic team!</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Comprehensive in-house and external training will be provided</li>\n  <li>Competitive remuneration package</li>\n  <li>Staffs Benefits</li>\n  <li>Located near MRT stations</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>RESPONSIBILITIES:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Oversee day-to-day Branch operations.</li>\n  <li>Responsible for all sales-related and telemarketing activities.</li>\n  <li>Meet branch sales quota.</li>\n  <li>Provide professional skin/body analysis and consultation.</li>\n  <li>Identify customer's needs and recommend suitable products and treatments to customers.</li>\n  <li>Perform facial, body hair removal and/or slimming treatments for customers (Extra points if you are able to).</li>\n  <li>Work closely with the Sales and Marketing Department on the execution of sales and promotion activities.</li>\n  <li>Assist in Management and Customer Service Relations process.</li>\n  <li>Handle customers feedback and service recovery.</li>\n  <li>Manage staff performance and discipline.</li>\n  <li>Working with operations to develop new treatments, protocols, packages to maximize profits.</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc duties assigned.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 2 - 3 years of relevant experience, in supervisory/managerial level.</li>\n  <li>Able to lead and manage a team.</li>\n  <li>Candidate who has a beauty/spa certified certificate will be an advantage. Eg. WSQ, CIBTAC , CIDESCO , ITEC.</li>\n  <li>Required Skill(s): Face, Body, Slimming &amp; Wellness consultation, Sales &amp; Operations of Branch, Customer Service, Relationship building with customers.</li>\n  <li>Good communications and interpersonal skills and service-oriented.</li>\n  <li>Positive working attitude and cheerful personality.</li>\n  <li>Friendly and caring towards customers and team.</li>\n  <li>Able to work well together with others.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The above responsibilities and job requirements will varies depending on your background and working experiences. We regret to inform that only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</p>",
